    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2011-09-23</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2011-10-07T22:07:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Tax Relief for Victims of Disasters Act of 2011 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to extend disaster-related tax provisions relating to the child tax credit and the earned income tax credit, losses, and the individual tax exemption to a qualified federally declared disaster individual (defined to mean, with respect to a federally declared disaster after December 31, 2010, and before January 1, 2013, any individual whose principal place of abode was located in the disaster area, who was displaced by the disaster, and who was performing employment services in the disaster area).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
